{"tid":2431153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會：63歲男子死亡與接種疫苗無直接關係","createTime":"2021-03-03T12:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T04:16:16.000Z","uid":350584,"like":38,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"3325ef89627aeb26810dc87440464245a59b505a","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:06:59.000Z","msg":"新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會下午就一名63歲男子，上周五接種科興新冠疫苗後，星期日出現急性呼吸困難到醫院求醫其後死亡的事件，召開緊急會議。<br />\n<br />\n專家委員會共同召集人孔繁毅於會後表示，病人本身有長期病患等問題，委員會審視資料後，認為死因同疫苗接種無直接關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578572-20210303.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578572-20210303.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=f989a0a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578572-20210303.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=86778ef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578572-20210303.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9d5145b38dbcd154350c6b6949ec1f7567b3c467","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:07:17.000Z","msg":"專家委員會共同召集人孔繁毅於會後表示，病人本身有長期病患等問題，委員會審視資料後，認為死因同疫苗接種無直接關係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451e7da4f66786768c9e9a493830441ec159fcc5","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:08:21.000Z","msg":"專家：唔關科興疫苗事"},{"pid":"ca84dbde743ea435cb32318c46d5e7437940a2cd","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"63歲長期病患男子接種科興疫苗兩天後死亡，專家委員會一致認為死亡與疫苗接種沒有直接關係。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局：已即時通報衞生署，不涉隱瞞。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌：男子接種疫苗後死亡，很大機會是心血管病導致。"},{"pid":"0ba6a0ccf5dc447a1227c4564a663b8b1c14ae74","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:10:49.000Z","msg":"許樹昌：男子接種疫苗後死亡，很大機會是心血管病導致。"},{"pid":"cfdee2838a8dbc1f8aa68b5f2d0731c82208fe10","tid":2431153,"uid":174013,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:10:50.000Z","msg":"GOOD NEWS<br />\n等睇班愛國愛黨藍絲廢老縮沙"},{"pid":"b8bebb29acb61cfd9a0c0cd9b8356a3a2866ca98","tid":2431153,"uid":60545,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"冇二百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a231d4c92afc5e1cc538b333a456909c3a3e9c","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"許生終於講野"},{"pid":"8f5aceacb12f7c6fea6f94e099f94eccf903672f","tid":2431153,"uid":2054,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4dMpyw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4dMpyw.png&h=edef39a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJXJrMR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJXJrMR.png&h=35e9362e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b8a593388d1c2cddba19603062bd74a138823bc","tid":2431153,"uid":90601,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:11:50.000Z","msg":"由誠信破產既政權講出黎話無關<br />\n同得人驚過佢直接認左佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2caeca8844f58e892345e9c5e5925ced6c9daa22","tid":2431153,"uid":33916,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"國安署列席你班 &quot;專家&quot; 夠膽話同科興有直接關係咩屌"},{"pid":"e9b983e39bcd741b3aeb0a15dd9e57fda7b38dc9","tid":2431153,"uid":54264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:12:32.000Z","msg":"見財化水"},{"pid":