示，這位病人患有嚴重冠心病，我們看到他三條心血管有嚴重閉塞，所以專家委員會一致認為死因與疫苗接種沒有直接關係，最有機會導致死亡原因病人的冠心病、以及急性心肌梗塞、肺水腫，導致他呼吸衰竭而死亡。」"},{"pid":"e9ac81eb38ea77bab64de52fed831d249541cf6c","tid":2431153,"uid":297609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:30:46.000Z","msg":"天才話，65都只係中年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f9d9ff55691811c82fb8549e69a669d62a0459","tid":2431153,"uid":100772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:31:13.000Z","msg":"死得好 人又冇錢又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be22f26866c107a5f3b0f55d92b16090c922c6ec","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:37:54.000Z","msg":"專家委員會：死亡個案與接種疫苗無直接關係 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381436&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=b1721dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381436</a>"},{"pid":"334e502edddd0508ebe05ff35195653b6a89c147","tid":2431153,"uid":276465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"藍絲們唔關事就快啲打反支啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94eaac98b3a98110986a7dab8571ff692cb0441a","tid":2431153,"uid":76135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"應該係因為佔中"},{"pid":"23916e542f7d3c064460fe4f276b01496f683bb7","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94eaac98b3a98110986a7dab8571ff692cb0441a","tid":2431153,"uid":76135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"應該係因為佔中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"咩都關佔中事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd0bc4e1b5718d120d37c2e319774b044ecc8e9","tid":2431153,"uid":32090