540\" />"},{"pid":"31ccd864959cc65a1ce8cb99e9d92e3b8650ce60","tid":2431153,"uid":311835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc7bea5451152bb518182f7c0385fa6d848aa4a4","tid":2431153,"uid":207792,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"怎麼才算打科興死?<br />\n<br />\n1.要在接種科興疫苗後立即死亡<br />\n2.要在身體狀態最好時接種<br />\n3.要吃早餐<br />\n4.你不能有糖尿病<br />\n5.你不能有高血壓<br />\n6.你不能心悸<br />\n7.你不能壓迫式防守，要給巴塞對於足夠的空間發揮<br />\n8.你不能擺鐵桶陣<br />\n9.在你的主場，你不能有主場哨，裁判要偏向巴塞，最好一開場就給主隊一張紅牌<br />\n10.美斯帶球，你不能幾個後衛去攔截，要讓美斯順利射門<br />\n11.你不能鏟美斯<br />\n12.你進的球前要把巴塞每個隊員都過一遍，最好把兩個門柱都過一遍，然後再把球踢進大門，這樣才是真水平，否則巴塞認為是靠運氣<br />\n13.你後衛在本方禁區不能開大腳<br />\n14.你要允許巴塞的教練中場休息進裁判室交流<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏球了，巴塞迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。巴塞迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏球。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"大哥才沒有輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6588b5049b6d85ef75af942ff16b379d978b884","tid":2431153,"uid":271742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f5aceacb12f7c6fea6f94e099f94eccf903672f","tid":2431153,"uid":2054,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4dMpyw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4dMpyw.png&h=edef39a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJXJrMR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJXJrMR.png&h=35e9362e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd6acea972e1e69a648dc74fec96dd143f74a0b","tid":2431153,"uid":89641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a08934803102f09594800b6cd9719362310c87c","tid":2431153,"uid":264887,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人問點解北京都建議60歲以上唔打得香港要打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:15:45.000Z","msg":"唔比60歲以上打，科興香港無人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e7f4bad3152100dbf2069b1b30933294f37794","tid":2431153,"uid":265524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fc7bea5451152bb518182f7c0385fa6d848aa4a4","tid":2431153,"uid":207792,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"怎麼才算打科興死?<br />\n<br />\n1.要在接種科興疫苗後立即死亡<br />\n2.要在身體狀態最好時接種<br />\n3.要吃早餐<br />\n4.你不能有糖尿病<br />\n5.你不能有高血壓<br />\n6.你不能心悸<br />\n7.你不能壓迫式防守，要給巴塞對於足夠的空間發揮<br />\n8.你不能擺鐵桶陣<br />\n9.在你的主場，你不能有主場哨，裁判要偏向巴塞，最好一開場就給主隊一張紅牌<br />\n10.美斯帶球，你不能幾個後衛去攔截，要讓美斯順利射門<br />\n11.你不能鏟美斯<br />\n12.你進的球前要把巴塞每個隊員都過一遍，最好把兩個門柱都過一遍，然後再把球踢進大門，這樣才是真水平，否則巴塞認為是靠運氣<br />\n13.你後衛在本方禁區不能開大腳<br />\n14.你要允許巴塞的教練中場休息進裁判室交流<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏球了，巴塞迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。巴塞迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏球。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:18:12.000Z","msg":"15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你打科興之後死了，專家委員會也會說你是自身狀況致死，說你是本身有病，說你沒有了解自己身體狀況。專家委員會總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不是因為打科興而死。"},{"pid":"91b327e80484f38f863bb7cafd146ff66b5b1f2c","tid":2431153,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"打針死咗要怪就怪自己身體弱<br />\nBy人民日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd5da9413a09254db2299e10edb160f11ae89d3","tid":2431153,"uid":89641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6a5622f8f86d80bf4b8810119708c224c279f7db","tid":2431153,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc7bea5451152bb518182f7c0385fa6d848aa4a4","tid":2431153,"uid":207792,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"怎麼才算打科興死?<br />\n<br />\n1.要在接種科興疫苗後立即死亡<br />\n2.要在身體狀態最好時接種<br />\n3.要吃早餐<br />\n4.你不能有糖尿病<br />\n5.你不能有高血壓<br />\n6.你不能心悸<br />\n7.你不能壓迫式防守，要給巴塞對於足夠的空間發揮<br />\n8.你不能擺鐵桶陣<br />\n9.在你的主場，你不能有主場哨，裁判要偏向巴塞，最好一開場就給主隊一張紅牌<br />\n10.美斯帶球，你不能幾個後衛去攔截，要讓美斯順利射門<br />\n11.你不能鏟美斯<br />\n12.你進的球前要把巴塞每個隊員都過一遍，最好把兩個門柱都過一遍，然後再把球踢進大門，這樣才是真水平，否則巴塞認為是靠運氣<br />\n13.你後衛在本方禁區不能開大腳<br />\n14.你要允許巴塞的教練中場休息進裁判室交流<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏球了，巴塞迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。巴塞迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏球。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"期待神人改埋後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"7.你不能有體內隱患，要驗屍時只找到科興疫苗影響為唯一死因<br />\n8.你不能生過病，講緊由細到大<br />\n9.你不可以有夜訓習慣，影響身體免疫力，陷國家於不義<br />\n10.近來幾個月你絕對沒有食過熱氣野，燥熱聽講科興抗體唔like<br />\n11.你沖完涼不可以風筒吹頭,有頭風好似係<br />\n12.打完乞嗤，你必須確保每次都有講「大吉利是」<br />\n13. 掃地一定係由大門向屋內掃，確保無掃走福氣，排除運氣影響你接種科興"},{"pid":"635593c0db07b294c8fba43d6297eb0bdb931000","tid":2431153,"uid":193969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fyHhwCM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfyHhwCM.png&h=fc37ce59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d724844397dbd2c5f60d34ddf99835c2bc51e2c3","tid":2431153,"uid":276090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"如果話呢個死同疫苗有關，咁中共既疫苗外交咪大撚鑊～ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8255d2a890246c790c90870a687cde79825304df","tid":2431153,"uid":324693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:26:58.000Z","msg":"呢班人渣專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0044141f5e09100df9f21b276ce5f8bbaa1c745a","tid":2431153,"uid":18772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:28:34.000Z","msg":"你要打科興自殺我唔會阻你<br />\n打咩針係有得揀既  <br />\nBIO N TECT打2針就有好大保護率"},{"pid":"eda404441dd71432af9451c101e42be74f799f19","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"孔繁毅：長期病患者若病情控制得宜適合接種疫苗<br />\n<br />\n新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會召開緊急會議，檢視一名63歲男子，上周五接種科興新冠疫苗後，星期日出現急性呼吸困難，到醫院求醫其後死亡的事件。專家委員會認為死因與疫苗接種無直接關係。"},{"pid":"df78b1df678a9fcd3ccb39ea2da5bcd059d2c155","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:36:35.000Z","msg":"孔繁毅說，是病人自己前往接種，護士有詢問有無過敏反應，但不會有如入院般查詢其病歷，病人接種後有等待30分鐘後才離開，認為並無出現行政漏洞。"},{"pid":"d5223ec101a9f81ac38281454781fb6b034bf41c","tid":2431153,"uid":81575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"認咗關事佢哋咪係殺人犯囉<br />\n<br />\n邊有人會認？！"},{"pid":"d30f1011c7c10086ad12e6a47a1335ec9a98a4fd","tid":2431153,"uid":117622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzYwBed.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzYwBed.gif&h=60f65c2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ad56097447fa225fb336b22cdf107c3c0116fab","tid":2431153,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"磚家：責任盡在死者，明知自己咁病，就唔好去打疫苗。"},{"pid":"e2fe7f2429eb39f3a341dca8a578da3007eccc65","tid":2431153,"uid":57946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d30f1011c7c10086ad12e6a47a1335ec9a98a4fd","tid":2431153,"uid":117622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzYwBed.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzYwBed.gif&h=60f65c2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T14:01:43.000Z","msg":"準備叫返佢賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e517e60001daf166355d3894766424a5c76f7b0a","tid":2431153,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bd5da9413a09254db2299e10edb160f11ae89d3","tid":2431153,"uid":89641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6a5622f8f86d80bf4b8810119708c224c279f7db","tid":2431153,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc7bea5451152bb518182f7c0385fa6d848aa4a4","tid":2431153,"uid":207792,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"怎麼才算打科興死?<br />\n<br />\n1.要在接種科興疫苗後立即死亡<br />\n2.要在身體狀態最好時接種<br />\n3.要吃早餐<br />\n4.你不能有糖尿病<br />\n5.你不能有高血壓<br />\n6.你不能心悸<br />\n7.你不能壓迫式防守，要給巴塞對於足夠的空間發揮<br />\n8.你不能擺鐵桶陣<br />\n9.在你的主場，你不能有主場哨，裁判要偏向巴塞，最好一開場就給主隊一張紅牌<br />\n10.美斯帶球，你不能幾個後衛去攔截，要讓美斯順利射門<br />\n11.你不能鏟美斯<br />\n12.你進的球前要把巴塞每個隊員都過一遍，最好把兩個門柱都過一遍，然後再把球踢進大門，這樣才是真水平，否則巴塞認為是靠運氣<br />\n13.你後衛在本方禁區不能開大腳<br />\n14.你要允許巴塞的教練中場休息進裁判室交流<br />\n15.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏球了，巴塞迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。巴塞迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏球。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"期待神人改埋後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"7.你不能有體內隱患，要驗屍時只找到科興疫苗影響為唯一死因<br />\n8.你不能生過病，講緊由細到大<br />\n9.你不可以有夜訓習慣，影響身體免疫力，陷國家於不義<br />\n10.近來幾個月你絕對沒有食過熱氣野，燥熱聽講科興抗體唔like<br />\n11.你沖完涼不可以風筒吹頭,有頭風好似係<br />\n12.打完乞嗤，你必須確保每次都有講「大吉利是」<br />\n13. 掃地一定係由大門向屋內掃，確保無掃走福氣，排除運氣影響你接種科興"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T14:01:43.000Z","msg":"12. 你接種的疫苗必須是兩劑以上，最好是全身都已經接種科興疫苗而死亡。這才是真的因為接種科興疫苗而死亡，否則疫苗專家認為死因是其他。<br />\n<br />\n14. 接種前必須先閱讀說明書，了解一切風險，並須得到醫生書面同意。<br />\n15. 接種時必須抱著興奮心情，要有相片或影片證明，否則影響疫苗效果。<br />\n16. 接種前先表示自己愛國愛黨，身為中國人應打中國貨，外國貨太多副作用。"},{"pid":"8f87287072f7db056e9bb256f1c58e816bb1b1d3","tid":2431153,"uid":336337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"無直接關係<br />\n你打完,頭暈又好,肚痛又好,到最後死左<br />\n都唔係直接關係,係間接關係<br />\n完"},{"pid":"cf2b1bf58bd74b20fda605d85b21d91f2eacc9dc","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d30f1011c7c10086ad12e6a47a1335ec9a98a4fd","tid":2431153,"uid":117622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzYwBed.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzYwBed.gif&h=60f65c2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T14:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0facbf409064fa8b5231040de7ebeedb2e5eee53","tid":2431153,"uid":1284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8f5aceacb12f7c6fea6f94e099f94eccf903672f","tid":2431153,"uid":2054,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4dMpyw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4dMpyw.png&h=edef39a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJXJrMR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJXJrMR.png&h=35e9362e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6SJsqx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6SJsqx.png&h=52a5ef16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75987e928dfd2a65dbeacb2ecb3c00b7aa01d1c9","tid":2431153,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T14:23:14.000Z","msg":"阿伯走得太前，越咗位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"ac30965f2bfa681bdc4bee42b7fe3318e57c13a2","tid":2431153,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會共同召集人孔繁毅：「根據病理學醫生初步解剖資料顯示，這位病人患有嚴重冠心病，我們看到他三條心血管有嚴重閉塞，所以專家委員會一致認為死因與疫苗接種沒有直接關係，最有機會導致死亡原因病人的冠心病、以及急性心肌梗塞、肺水腫，導致他呼吸衰竭而死亡。」"}}